There are emerging indications that one of the best newscasters and programme presenters with the Television Continental (TVC), Ngozi Alaegbu, has resigned from the service of the media organization. The information on her resignation began to spread on Thursday; however, the details are yet to be revealed on the circumstances of her resignation.
She has been a renowned broadcaster with the TVC with sound presentation of news and public issues, particularly, on TVC morning shows and newscast in later hours.

			
